ItemDef.def:Label: Date of Last Exposure to Treatment

ItemDef.Name: ASTDT
ItemDef.Comment: AE.AESTDTC, converted to a numeric SAS date. Some events with partial dates are imputed in a conservative manner. If the day component is missing, a value of '01' is used. If both the month and day are missing no imputation is performed as these dates clearly indicate a start prior to the beginning of treatment. There are no events with completely missing start dates.
ItemDef.def:Label: Analysis Start Date

ItemDef.Name: ASTDTF
ItemDef.Comment: ASTDTF='D' if the day value within the character date is imputed. Note that only day values needed to be imputed for this study.
ItemDef.def:Label: Analysis Start Date Imputation Flag

ItemDef.Name: ASTDY
ItemDef.Comment: IF ASTDT>=TRTSDT>MISSING then ASTDY=ASTDT-TRTSDT+1 Else if TRTSDT>ASTDT>MISSING then ASTDY=ASTDT-TRTSDT
ItemDef.def:Label: Analysis Start Relative Day

ItemDef.Name: AENDT
ItemDef.Comment: AE.AEENDTC, converted to a numeric SAS date
ItemDef.def:Label: Analysis End Date

ItemDef.Name: AENDY
ItemDef.Comment: IF AENDT>=TRTSDT>MISSING then AENDY=AENDT-TRTSDT+1 Else if TRTSDT>AENDT>MISSING then AENDY=AENDT-TRTSDT
ItemDef.def:Label: Analysis End Relative Day

ItemDef.Name: ADURU
ItemDef.Comment: If ADURN is not missing then ADURU='DAY'
ItemDef.def:Label: AE Duration Units

ItemDef.Name: AETERM
ItemDef.def:Label: Reported Term for the Adverse Event

ItemDef.Name: TRTEMFL
ItemDef.Comment: If ASTDT >= TRTSDT > . then TRTEMFL='Y'. Otherwise TRTEMFL='N'
ItemDef.def:Label: Treatment Emergent Analysis Flag

ItemDef.Name: AOCCFL
ItemDef.Comment: Subset to TRTEMFL='Y' and sort by Subject (USUBJID), Start Date (ASTDT), and Sequence Number (AESEQ) and flag the first record (set AOCCFL=Y) within each Subject
ItemDef.def:Label: 1st Occurrence of Any AE Flag

ItemDef.Name: AOCCSFL
ItemDef.Comment: Subset to TRTEMFL='Y' and sort by Subject (USUBJID), System Organ Class (AEBODSYS), Start Date (ASTDT), and Sequence Number (AESEQ) and flag the first record (set AOCCSFL=Y) within each Subject and SOC
ItemDef.def:Label: 1st Occurrence of SOC Flag

ItemDef.Name: AOCCPFL
ItemDef.Comment: Subset to TRTEMFL='Y' and sort by Subject (USUBJID), System Organ Class (AEBODSYS), Preferred Term (AEDECOD), Start Date (ASTDT), and Sequence Number (AESEQ) and flag the first record (set AOCCPFL=Y) within each Subject, SOC, and PT
ItemDef.def:Label: 1st Occurrence of Preferred Term Flag

ItemDef.Name: AOCC02FL
ItemDef.Comment: Subset to TRTEMFL='Y' and AESER='Y' and sort by Subject (USUBJID), Start Date (ASTDT), and Sequence Number (AESEQ) and flag the first record (set AOCC02FL=Y) within each Subject
ItemDef.def:Label: 1st Occurrence 02 Flag for Serious

ItemDef.Name: AOCC03FL
ItemDef.Comment: Subset to TRTEMFL='Y' and AESER='Y' and sort by Subject (USUBJID), System Organ Class (AEBODSYS), Start Date (ASTDT), and Sequence Number (AESEQ) and flag the first record (set AOCC03FL=Y) within each Subject and SOC
ItemDef.def:Label: 1st Occurrence 03 Flag for Serious SOC

ItemDef.Name: AOCC04FL
ItemDef.Comment: Subset to TRTEMFL='Y' and AESER='Y' and sort by Subject (USUBJID), System Organ Class (AEBODSYS), Preferred Term (AEDECOD), Start Date (ASTDT), and Sequence Number (AESEQ) and flag the first record (set AOCC04FL=Y) within each Subject, SOC, and PT
ItemDef.def:Label: 1st Occurrence 04 Flag for Serious PT

ItemDef.Name: CQ01NAM
ItemDef.Comment: If AEDECOD contains any of the character strings of ('APPLICATION', 'DERMATITIS', 'ERYTHEMA', 'BLISTER') OR if AEBODSYS='SKIN AND SUBC UTANEOUS TISSUE DISORDERS' but AEDECOD is not in ('COLD SWEAT', 'HYPERHIDROSIS', 'ALOPECIA') then CQ01NAM='DERMATOLOGIC EVENTS' Otherwise CQ01NAM=NULL
ItemDef.def:Label: Customized Query 01 Name

ItemDef.Name: AOCC01FL
ItemDef.Comment: Subset to CQ01NAM='' and TRTEMFL='Y' and sort by Subject (USUBJID), Start Date (ASTDT), and Sequence Number (AESEQ) and flag the first record (set AOCC01FL=Y) within each Subject (Flag First Treatment Emergent Dermatological Event for Time to Event Analysis)
ItemDef.def:Label: 1st Occurrence 01 Flag for CQ01

ItemDef.Comment: TRT01A=TRT01P, i.e., no difference between actual and randomized treatment in this study.

ItemDef.Name: TRTEDT
ItemDef.Comment: The date of final dose (from the CRF) is EX.EXENDTC on the subject's last EX record. If the date of final dose is missing for the subject and the subject discontinued after visit 3, use the date of discontinuation as the date of last dose. Convert the date to a SAS date.
ItemDef.def:Label: Date of Last Exposure to Treatment

ItemDef.Name: CUMDOSE
ItemDef.Comment: For ARMN=0 or 1: CUMDOSE=TRT01PN*TRTDUR. --- For ARMN=2: CUMDOSE will be based on 54mg per day for the # of days subj was in 1st dosing interval (i.e., visit4date-TRTSTDT+1 if 1st interval completed, TRTEDT-TRTSTDT+1 if subj discontinued <=visit 4 and > visit 3), 81mg per day for the # of days subj was in 2nd dosing interval (i.e., visit12date-visit4date if 2nd interval completed, TRTEDT-visit4date if subj discontinued <= visit 12 and > visit 4), and 54mg per day for the # of days subj was in 3rd dosing interval (i.e., TRTEDT - visit12date if subj continued after visit 12).
ItemDef.def:Label: Cumulative Dose (as planned)

ItemDef.Name: AGEGR1N
ItemDef.Comment: AGEGR1 = 1 if AGE <65. AGEGR1 = 2 if AGE 65-80. AGEGR1 = 3 if AGE >80.
ItemDef.def:Label: Pooled Age Group 1 (N)

ItemDef.Name: SAFFL
ItemDef.Comment: Y if ITTFL='Y' and TRTSDT ne missing. N otherwise
ItemDef.def:Label: Safety Population Flag

ItemDef.Name: ITTFL
ItemDef.Comment: Y if ARMCD ne ' '. N otherwise
ItemDef.def:Label: Intent-To-Treat Population Flag

ItemDef.Name: EFFFL
ItemDef.Comment: Y if SAFFL='Y AND subject has at least one record in QS for ADAS-Cog with VISITNUM>3 AND at least one record in QS for CIBIC+ with VISITNUM>3, N otherwise
ItemDef.def:Label: Efficacy Population Flag

ItemDef.Name: COMP8FL

ItemDef.Name: COMP16FL

ItemDef.Name: COMP24FL
